title: Fantasy Book v5#1 (#19) 1986-03
description:
Fantasy Book Vol. 5 No. 1 (whole issue 19), March 1986.

This magazine is a fantasy and science fiction anthology (ISSN 0277-0717) edited by Dennis Mallonee, Nick Smith, Forrest J. Ackerman, Jessica Salmonson, and Darrell Schweitzer which I have reproduced here as an OCR'd PDF. Contents:

Hartmann, Thom: Beetle Black for Death
Hussey, Leigh Ann: The Lover of Lord Eithras
Lackey, Mercedes: The Archivist
Lackey, Mercedes: Blind Desire
Linzner, Gordon: The Spirit of West 76th
Petaja, Emil: The Mist
Sherman, Cordelia: The Fleeting Season
Stuart, Kiel: Green Fire
Turtledove, Harry: Thicker Than Water
Zimmer, Paul Edwin: A Swordsman from Carcosa, Part I
